file`\n37:   - Verification: `grep \"ldflags=\\\"-w -s\\\"\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"go build\" docker/Dockerfile`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Create runtime stage with alpine:3.19 base\n40:   - Purpose: Define minimal runtime base image\n41:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n42:   - Verification: `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Add ca-certificates and tzdata packages\n45:   - Purpose: Install TLS certs and timezone data\n46:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n47:   - Verification: `grep \"apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata\" docker/Dockerfile`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Create non-root user apiserver (UID 1000)\n50:   - Purpose: Add security through non-root execution\n51:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n52:   - Verification: `grep \"adduser -D -u 1000 apiserver\" docker/Dockerfile`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.8**: COPY binary from builder stage to runtime\n55:   - Purpose: Extract compiled binary from builder\n56:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n57:   - Verification: `grep \"COPY --from=builder\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"workloadmanager\" docker/Dockerfile`\n58: \n59: - [ ] **T1.9**: Set USER 1000 and EXPOSE 8080\n60:   - Purpose: Configure security context and port\n61:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n62:   - Verification: `grep \"USER 1000\" docker/Dockerfile && grep \"EXPOSE 8080\" docker/Dockerfile`\n63: \n64: - [ ] **T1.10**: Set ENTRYPOINT for workloadmanager binary\n65:   - Purpose: Define container entrypoint\n66:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n67:   - Verification: `grep \"ENTRYPOINT \\[\\\"/app/bin/workloadmanager\\\"\\]\" docker/Dockerfile`\n68: \n69: ### Phase 2: Router Dockerfile Foundation (ST-2)\n70: \n71: - [ ] **T2.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24-alpine base\n72:   - Purpose: Define builder stage for Go compilation\n73:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n74:   - Verification: `grep \"FROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n75: \n76: - [ ] **T2.2**: Add go.mod/go.sum COPY and cache mount for module download\n77:   - Purpose: Optimize module download with BuildKit cache\n78:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n79:   - Verification: `grep \"RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T2.3**: Add source COPY including client-go/\n82:   - Purpose: Include client-go module for router\n83:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n84:   - Verification: `grep \"COPY client-go/ client-go/\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n85: \n86: - [ ] **T2.4**: Add CGO_ENABLED=0 and go build with ldflags\n87:   - Purpose: Build optimized router binary\n88:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n89:   - Verification: `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile.router && grep \"./cmd/router\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n90: \n91: - [ ] **T2.5**: Create runtime stage with alpine:3.19 base\n92:   - Purpose: Define minimal runtime base image\n93:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n94:   - Verification: `grep \"FROM alpine:3.19\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n95: \n96: - [ ] **T2.6**: Add ca-certificates, tzdata, and non-root user router (UID 1000)\n97:   - Purpose: Install packages and create security user\n98:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n99:   - Verification: `grep \"adduser -D -u 1000 router\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n100: \n101: - [ ] **T2.7**: COPY router binary from builder and set USER 1000\n102:   - Purpose: Extract binary and configure security\n103:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n104:   - Verification: `grep \"/app/bin/router\" docker/Dockerfile.router && grep \"USER 1000\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n105: \n106: - [ ] **T2.8**: Set EXPOSE 8080 and ENTRYPOINT for router binary\n107:   - Purpose: Configure port and entrypoint\n108:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n109:   - Verification: `grep \"ENTRYPOINT \\[\\\"/app/bin/router\\\"\\]\" docker/Dockerfile.router`\n110: \n111: ### Phase 3: PicoD Dockerfile Foundation (ST-3)\n112: \n113: - [ ] **T3.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24 base (not