CGO, ldflags, cache mounts, user security"},"output":"5. Check CGO_ENABLED=0 (static compilation):\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has CGO_ENABLED=0\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has CGO_ENABLED=0\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod has CGO_ENABLED=0\n\n6. Check ldflags optimization (-w -s):\n    go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/workloadmanager ./cmd/workload-manager\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has ldflags\n    go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/router ./cmd/router\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has ldflags\nRUN go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod has ldflags\n\n7. Check BuildKit cache mounts (Alpine Dockerfiles):\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has cache mounts\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has cache mounts\n\n8. Check USER directive (security):\nUSER 1000\n  ‚úì Dockerfile runs as non-root (UID 1000)\nUSER 1000\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router runs as non-root (UID 1000)\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod runs as root (no USER directive)\n","metadata":{"output":"5. Check CGO_ENABLED=0 (static compilation):\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has CGO_ENABLED=0\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has CGO_ENABLED=0\nENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod has CGO_ENABLED=0\n\n6. Check ldflags optimization (-w -s):\n    go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/workloadmanager ./cmd/workload-manager\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has ldflags\n    go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/router ./cmd/router\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has ldflags\nRUN go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -trimpath -o /app/bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod has ldflags\n\n7. Check BuildKit cache mounts (Alpine Dockerfiles):\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n  ‚úì Dockerfile has cache mounts\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router has cache mounts\n\n8. Check USER directive (security):\nUSER 1000\n  ‚úì Dockerfile runs as non-root (UID 1000)\nUSER 1000\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.router runs as non-root (UID 1000)\n  ‚úì Dockerfile.picod runs as root (no USER directive)\n","exit":0,"description":"Verify CGO, ldflags, cache mounts, user security","truncated":false},"title":"Verify CGO, ldflags, cache mounts, user security","time":{"start":1775886840419,"end":1775886840553}}}}
